###< doctrine/doctrine-bundle ###

###> symfony/messenger ###
MESSENGER_TRANSPORT_DSN=doctrine://default?auto_setup=0
###< symfony/messenger ###

###> app/security ###
DEFAULT_USER_PASSWORD=password123
###< app/security ###
